00:36:15,200 --> 00:36:17,330
a version of a rotation operator

864
00:36:17,330 --> 00:36:18,670
for very small rotation.

865
00:36:20,510 --> 00:36:23,430
Let's consider the commutator.

866
00:36:24,090 --> 00:36:24,610
Okay.

867
00:36:26,350 --> 00:36:28,610
What the commutator is telling us about

868
00:36:28,610 --> 00:36:30,650
